1002
00:57:35,250 --> 00:57:37,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini hari keberuntunganmu.</font>

1003
00:57:38,720 --> 00:57:41,319
<font color=#FFFF00>Gye Hwa, dasar gila...</font>

1004
00:57:42,089 --> 00:57:45,629
