1011
00:58:21,829 --> 00:58:24,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Di mana perhiasan itu?</font>

1012
00:58:29,910 --> 00:58:32,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Hai, Deul Lae. Kamu menemukan perhiasannya?</font>

1013
00:58:33,579 --> 00:58:35,079
